ruby-erubis (2.7.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release (Closes: #657127)
  * Switch to the gem2deb helper and follow new policy (Closes: #657141)
    - Rename source package to ruby-erubis
    - Rename main binary package to ruby-erubis and make the other one
      transitional
    - Put under the Debian Ruby Extras team maintenance
    - Use ruby dh sequence
  * Switch to dpkg-source 3.0 (quilt) format
  * debian/copyright: Use DEP5 specification
  * debian/watch: Use pkg-ruby-extras helper

